                        <p class="hint-complete" id="hint-complete">
                            ‚úÖ Du har sett alla ledtr√•dar! F√∂rs√∂k nu skriva in svaret.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- FRAMG√ÖNG -->
                <div class="success-section" id="success">
