    <div class="page-container">
        <nav class="sidebar">
            <div class="sidebar-title">Inneh√•ll</div>
            <ul class="nav-list">
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="index.html" class="nav-link">‚Üê Tillbaka</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="uppgift-06-lagga-ihop-brak.html" class="nav-link completed">6. L√§gga ihop br√•k</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="uppgift-07-dra-bort-brak.html" class="nav-link completed">7. Dra bort br√•k</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a href="#" class="nav-link current">8. Blandad form<span class="you-are-here">‚Üê Du √§r h√§r</span></a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="uppgift-09-forlanga-brak.html" class="nav-link">9. F√∂rl√§nga br√•k</a></li>
