            <div class="sidebar-title">Inneh√•ll</div>
            <ul class="nav-list">
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="index.html" class="nav-link">‚Üê Tillbaka</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="uppgift-15-hitta-procenten.html" class="nav-link completed">15. Hitta procenten</a></li>
