                    </p>

                    <div class="task-problem">1/4 = ?</div>

                    <div class="answer-options">
                        <button class="option-btn" onclick="checkOption(this, true)">0,25</button>
                        <button class="option-btn" onclick="checkOption(this, false)">0,4</button>
