                <li class="nav-item"><a href="index.html" class="nav-link">‚Üê Tillbaka</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="uppgift-26-20-procent.html" class="nav-link completed">26. R√§kna 20%</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="uppgift-27-25-procent.html" class="nav-link completed">27. R√§kna 25%</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a href="#" class="nav-link current">28. Rabatt i procent<span class="you-are-here">‚Üê Du √§r h√§r</span></a>
