                        <br>Vad √§r det nya priset?
                    </p>

                    <div class="task-problem">
                        Rabatt: 50% av 60 kr = 30 kr
                        <br>Nytt pris: 60 - 30 = ?
                    </div>

                    <div class="answer-input-container">
                        <input type="text" id="answer" class="answer-input" maxlength="3" placeholder="?" aria-label="Svar">
                        <span class="unit-label">kr</span>
